                  <summary>I) Haymanotä ʾabaw “Faith of the Fathers” (fols. 3r-133rc)&#xD; II)
                     Maṣḥafa ṭomār “Book of the Letter (from Heaven)” (133rc-135rb)&#xD; - Table of
                     contents (fols. 135rb-135vb)&#xD; &#xD; Colophon.</summary>
